msgctxt "1296"
msgid "Quickturns"
msgstr "Inversioni rapide"

msgctxt "56_Quickturns"
msgid ""
"Quickturns can be used during chase events as a technique to round corners "
"without losing speed. This technique comes in handy in areas with many "
"corners, such as rooftops."
msgstr ""
"Le Svolte Rapide possono essere usate durante gli inseguimenti come tecnica "
"per curvare senza perdere velocità. Questa tecnica è utile in aree con molte"
" curve, come i tetti."

msgctxt "68_Quickturns"
msgid ""
"Quickturns are executed by <Color:7>using "
"<Color:Default><Action:Button_LS_Up@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Down@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Left@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Right@Chase><Color:7>"
" while pressing<Color:Default> <Action:Button_R1@Chase>."
msgstr ""
"Le Svolte Rapide si eseguono <Color:7>usando "
"<Color:Default><Action:Button_LS_Up@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Down@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Left@Chase><Action:Button_LS_Right@Chase><Color:7>"
" mentre si tiene premuto<Color:Default> <Action:Button_R1@Chase>."

msgctxt "80_Quickturns"
msgid ""
"This information has been added as a <Color:14>memo<Color:Default>. "
"Read <Color:14>memos<Color:Default> by selecting <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> in the Pause Menu. "
"You can access the Pause Menu with the <Action:Button_Options@Adventure> button."
msgstr ""
"Questa informazione è stata aggiunta come <Color:14>Memo<Color:Default>. "
"Leggi i <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> selezionando <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> nel menu di Pausa. "
